            . The prosecutor came into the prisoner's house: he sat down, and asked me if Mr. Bourn was within: I said, no, but I expected him home very soon: we asked him, if he would drink; he did: he said, he was robbed in this house. After coming from the Justice's, we brought him into the room: we asked him, if that was the room he was robbed in: he said, he believed it was. </p>
